text: Oink Oink.. I know that it can be Hard sometimes.. the expectations that comes from all kinds of People.. from the Lows to the Highs.. from the dumbest people to the smartest people.. YOUNG and Old People.. and the Bars are very high for those who are watching YOU from the Side line.. so many fans are screaming.. crying and weeping.. moved by the Hearts because being truly inspired.. Four Asian girls.. three Koreans and one THAI.. coming from different background but one thing in Common.. Dreams.. Your Hearts are Big and Your Dreams are Big too.. Odds were against YOU.. People saying to Give UP.. and so Many negative remarks made.. But.. when Your Hearts are strong.. and Dreams are so Big.. and the determination of Never giving UP.. and times when YOU do want to Give UP comes in questions.. I want to tell YOU this.. Look how far YOU came.. LOOK at how many valley lows YOU have to cross and How many Mountain TOPS you had to climb to reach where YOU are today.. it is because the Four Most Beautiful Flowers held their hands together.. there will be tears and fears.. sorrows and pains YOU must learn to endure.. and to be patient with each Other.. LOOK how far YOU came.. it is because UNITY.. together.. going through together kept YOU so strong.. I know it feels like when it be Over.. because it grows tired and harder as time goes by and as YOU are aging.. as YOU are growing older together.. if there are times you want to give UP.. LOOK at How far YOU.. the four Most Beautiful Flowers.. how you had to crawl.. to walk.. and Now running together.. there are so many people in this Life who don't have another friend anymore.. too many people are alone and many are getting lonelier.. but.. at least the four most Beautiful Flower.. when YOU had to walk and run.. over come with time endurance and patient.. YOU have a friend.. and also sisters that not Money can buy.. a true and real friendship that ONLY TIME can bring together.. when it rains.. you girls walked together in that rain.. and stood through time and patient.. a real friendship and sisterhood is better than having NONE.. memories are being shared and growing together.. as we all grow old.. at least.. As an Asian.. YOU are sharing that Asians can Dream BIG.. and to have a strong Heart.. to be courageous and to take risks on uncertain times.. that is WHY it made YOU the Biggest.. the Best.. all TIME the NUMBER ONE.. because it all happened at uncertain times.. when YOU had very small chance to succeed.. NO ONE really knew about K - POP.. NOW... so many people has opened UP to the Music and trying to learn about the language and the culture.. the BUILDERS.. so be proud of what YOU have created today.. that Now.. many Asian Boys and girls can dream.. when they have a strong Heart and a Big Dream.. things can happen and that is what YOU have put into the Hearts of many who feels impossible.. YOU have opened a door when people thought it was IMPOSSIBLE to Open.. the One who dreams BIGGER.. creates and gives HOPES and Dreams to the People who are lessor in this Life.. who feels so small.. just wanted to say.. THANK YOU for being truly successful and giving people Dreams to dream Bigger.. YOU are One of a KIND.. just a BLESSING in this life.. the four Most Beautiful Flowers.. me Dandelions.. the world top best.. greatest and the most inspiring and amazing.. the NUMBER ONE..
